::Dark One::

The CR chamber's door closes behind Squizzy, Dark One walking over to a panel 
and pressing a few buttons. The CR chamber was one designed for hostages and 
prisoners, and put the occupant into stasis. He activates the cyber-liquid, 
designed to knock out the occupant. Tapping a few more keys, he locks the CR 
door.

"If she tries to escape, shoot her untill she's out," he orders the autoguns, 
running out of the room and heading for the exit of the Alliance base.
